 \"endedAt\": 1776215807993,\n      \"runtimeMs\": 9291,\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"lastTo\": \"heartbeat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/bca9bbb9-d1eb-408d-9e3d-14dd521dcc45.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"user\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"text\",\n              \"text\": \"System: [2026-04-15 00:48:28 UTC] The telegram:group:-5163901258 session is unresponsive (timed out). The delivery failed — the session appears to have ended silently despite showing \\\"running\\\" in the session list.\\nSystem: \\nSystem: **Note for Lead:** Telegram delivery to group -5163901258 failed — the group session has become stale/unresponsive. The report that should have been sent was:\\nSystem: \\nSystem: > 🟡 Orbis — 5p Update | 00:46 UTC 15 Apr\\nSystem: > Changes detected:\\nSystem: > • RECOVERED: telegram:direct:6053576134 — new instance online since 22:15 UTC (prior instance ended 22:02 UTC)\\nSystem: > Pipeline: HEALTHY ✅\\nSystem: > • Active sessions: 4 (cron:ed2d0b5d ✅ cron:e7885813 ✅ cron:6f3323ef ✅ telegram:direct ✅)\\nSystem: > • MCP: stitch ✅ confluence ✅ gitlab ✅\\nSystem: > • Cron: 5p progress ✅ | Daily @ 5AM+7 ✅\\nSystem: > • Blockers: none\\nSystem: > — Orbis 🌐\\nSystem: \\nSystem: `heartbeat-state.json` updated. Silent for next cycle unless something new changes.\\nSystem: [2026-04-15 00:50:18 UTC] Pipeline stable. No changes since last report (00:46 UTC). Silent exit.\\nSystem: [2026-04-15 00:53:58 UTC] Report delivered via cron mechanism (agentTurn output → Telegram channel delivery).\\nSystem: \\nSystem: **Summary:**\\nSystem: - 🟡 **5p Update sent** to group -5163901258 at 00:51 UTC\\nSystem: - **Change:** main session ended normally\\nSystem: - **Pipeline:** HEALTHY ✅ | 3 active crons | MCP all ✅ | Blockers: none\\nSystem: - Heartbeat state updated to `memor